-----------------------------------------
  Kobe Product Run Setting
-----------------------------------------

./full : full size setting
./mini : 1/6 size of full setting

* each directory includes config, init, input, and run directories.

* config directory includes all config files to run the test case.

* init, input, and run directories include job-scripts to submit jobs on K computer.
  run directory has five scripts; single.*** scritps are single domain test for each domains,
  and run.nest.sh script is for a online-nesting test.
